{
  "video_id": "cJg_tPB0Nu0",
  "title": "The birth of virtual reality as an art form | Chris Milk",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 14134.0,
      "end_time": 15293.0,
      "text": "When I was a kid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15317.0,
      "end_time": 17825.0,
      "text": "I experienced something so powerful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17849.0,
      "end_time": 20923.0,
      "text": "I spent the rest of my life searching for it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20947.0,
      "end_time": 22459.0,
      "text": "and in all the wrong places."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23327.0,
      "end_time": 25920.0,
      "text": "What I experienced wasn&#39;t virtual reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26633.0,
      "end_time": 27816.0,
      "text": "It was music."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28251.0,
      "end_time": 30547.0,
      "text": "And this is where the story begins."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31797.0,
      "end_time": 33167.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33191.0,
      "end_time": 35137.0,
      "text": "listening to the Beatles&#39; \"White Album.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35161.0,
      "end_time": 38329.0,
      "text": "And the look on my face is the feeling"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38353.0,
      "end_time": 41990.0,
      "text": "that I&#39;ve been searching for ever since."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41938.0,
      "end_time": 44524.0,
      "text": "Music goes straight to the emotional vein,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44548.0,
      "end_time": 46154.0,
      "text": "into your bloodstream"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46178.0,
      "end_time": 47509.0,
      "text": "and right into your heart."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48157.0,
      "end_time": 50678.0,
      "text": "It deepens every experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51717.0,
      "end_time": 52882.0,
      "text": "Fellas?"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 53454.0,
      "end_time": 57672.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 59472.0,
      "end_time": 61624.0,
      "text": "This is the amazing McKenzie Stubbert"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 61648.0,
      "end_time": 63527.0,
      "text": "and Joshua Roman."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 63551.0,
      "end_time": 64714.0,
      "text": "Music --"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 64738.0,
      "end_time": 65932.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 65956.0,
      "end_time": 67114.0,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 68630.0,
      "end_time": 72455.0,
      "text": "Music makes everything have more emotional resonance."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 73229.0,
      "end_time": 75158.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s see how it does for this talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 75825.0,
      "end_time": 79569.0,
      "text": "The right piece of music at the right time fuses with us"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 79593.0,
      "end_time": 80918.0,
      "text": "on a cellular level."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 81382.0,
      "end_time": 83662.0,
      "text": "When I hear that one song"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 84502.0,
      "end_time": 85804.0,
      "text": "from that one summer"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 86488.0,
      "end_time": 87665.0,
      "text": "with that one girl,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 88480.0,
      "end_time": 90501.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m instantly transported back there again."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 91963.0,
      "end_time": 93130.0,
      "text": "Hey, Stacey."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 94908.0,
      "end_time": 98186.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s a part of the story, though, where I got a little greedy."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 98210.0,
      "end_time": 101808.0,
      "text": "I thought if I added more layers on top of the music,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 102394.0,
      "end_time": 105646.0,
      "text": "I could make the feelings even more powerful."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 105670.0,
      "end_time": 108504.0,
      "text": "So I got into directing music videos."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 109432.0,
      "end_time": 110906.0,
      "text": "This is what they looked like."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 114429.0,
      "end_time": 115672.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s my brother, Jeff."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 116799.0,
      "end_time": 118121.0,
      "text": "Sorry about this, Jeff."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 118145.0,
      "end_time": 119232.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 119256.0,
      "end_time": 121203.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s me, just so we&#39;re even."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 122682.0,
      "end_time": 123885.0,
      "text": "Incredible moves."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 124444.0,
      "end_time": 125785.0,
      "text": "Should&#39;ve been a dancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 125809.0,
      "end_time": 126931.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 126955.0,
      "end_time": 128267.0,
      "text": "These experiments grew,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 128291.0,
      "end_time": 131750.0,
      "text": "and in time, started to look more like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 133852.0,
      "end_time": 136492.0,
      "text": "In both, I&#39;m searching for the same thing, though,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 136516.0,
      "end_time": 139174.0,
      "text": "to capture that lightning in a bottle."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 140192.0,
      "end_time": 141865.0,
      "text": "Except, I&#39;m not."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 141889.0,
      "end_time": 145448.0,
      "text": "Adding moving pictures over the music added narrative dimension, yes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 146261.0,
      "end_time": 148785.0,
      "text": "but never quite equated the power"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 148809.0,
      "end_time": 151553.0,
      "text": "that just raw music had for me on its own."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 152795.0,
      "end_time": 155948.0,
      "text": "This is not a great thing to realize when you&#39;ve devoted your life"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 155973.0,
      "end_time": 158812.0,
      "text": "and professional career to becoming a music video director."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 158836.0,
      "end_time": 161137.0,
      "text": "I kept asking myself, did I take the wrong path?"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 162353.0,
      "end_time": 166204.0,
      "text": "So I started thinking: if I could involve you, the audience, more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 166228.0,
      "end_time": 169230.0,
      "text": "I might be able to make you feel something more as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 169901.0,
      "end_time": 173860.0,
      "text": "So Aaron Koblin and I began auditioning new technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 173110.0,
      "end_time": 176248.0,
      "text": "that could put more of you inside of the work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 176272.0,
      "end_time": 179905.0,
      "text": "like your childhood home in \"The Wilderness Downtown,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 180750.0,
      "end_time": 184510.0,
      "text": "your hand-drawn portraits, in \"The Johnny Cash Project,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 185581.0,
      "end_time": 186981.0,
      "text": "and your interactive dreams"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 187791.0,
      "end_time": 189488.0,
      "text": "in \"3 Dreams of Black.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 191469.0,
      "end_time": 193426.0,
      "text": "We were pushing beyond the screen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 193450.0,
      "end_time": 195430.0,
      "text": "trying to connect more deeply"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 195455.0,
      "end_time": 197832.0,
      "text": "to people&#39;s hearts and imaginations."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 198745.0,
      "end_time": 200910.0,
      "text": "But it wasn&#39;t quite enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 201258.0,
      "end_time": 206570.0,
      "text": "It still didn&#39;t have the raw experiential power of pure music for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 207443.0,
      "end_time": 209504.0,
      "text": "So I started chasing a new technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 209528.0,
      "end_time": 212227.0,
      "text": "that I only had read about in science fiction."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 212826.0,
      "end_time": 215234.0,
      "text": "And after years of searching, I found a prototype."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 215871.0,
      "end_time": 220950.0,
      "text": "It was a project from Nonny de la Peña in Mark Bolas&#39;s lab in USC."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 221102.0,
      "end_time": 224170.0,
      "text": "And when I tried it, I knew I&#39;d found it."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 225950.0,
      "end_time": 226587.0,
      "text": "I could taste the lightning."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 227334.0,
      "end_time": 228984.0,
      "text": "It was called virtual reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 230470.0,
      "end_time": 232303.0,
      "text": "This was it five years ago when I ran into it."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 233530.0,
      "end_time": 235592.0,
      "text": "This is what it looks like now."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 236846.0,
      "end_time": 240751.0,
      "text": "I quickly started building things in this new medium,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 240775.0,
      "end_time": 242992.0,
      "text": "and through that process we realized something:"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 243664.0,
      "end_time": 247810.0,
      "text": "that VR is going to play an incredibly important role"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 247105.0,
      "end_time": 248820.0,
      "text": "in the history of mediums."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 249681.0,
      "end_time": 252398.0,
      "text": "In fact, it&#39;s going to be the last one."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 253390.0,
      "end_time": 257500.0,
      "text": "I mean this because it&#39;s the first medium that actually makes the jump"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 257290.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260317.00000000003,
      "text": "from our internalization of an author&#39;s expression"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 260341.0,
      "end_time": 262110.0,
      "text": "of an experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 262350.0,
      "end_time": 264687.0,
      "text": "to our experiencing it firsthand."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 265691.0,
      "end_time": 267854.0,
      "text": "You look confused. I&#39;ll explain. Don&#39;t worry."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 267879.0,
      "end_time": 269273.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 269830.0,
      "end_time": 273200.0,
      "text": "If we go back to the origins of mediums,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 273440.0,
      "end_time": 274407.0,
      "text": "by all best guesses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 274432.0,
      "end_time": 277398.0,
      "text": "it starts around a fire, with a good story."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 277986.0,
      "end_time": 279450.0,
      "text": "Our clan leader is telling us"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 279475.0,
      "end_time": 283104.0,
      "text": "about how he hunted the woolly mammoth on the tundra that day."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 284690.0,
      "end_time": 285408.0,
      "text": "We hear his words"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 286900.0,
      "end_time": 289363.0,
      "text": "and translate them into our own internal truths."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 290839.0,
      "end_time": 292400.0,
      "text": "The same thing happens"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 292280.0,
      "end_time": 294670.0,
      "text": "when we look at the cave painting version of the story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 296241.0,
      "end_time": 297824.0,
      "text": "the book about the mammoth hunt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 298472.0,
      "end_time": 299705.0,
      "text": "the play,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 300109.0,
      "end_time": 301294.0,
      "text": "the radio broadcast,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 301749.0,
      "end_time": 302914.0,
      "text": "the television show"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 303582.0,
      "end_time": 304736.0,
      "text": "or the movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 305532.0,
      "end_time": 309264.0,
      "text": "All of these mediums require what we call \"suspension of disbelief,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 309288.0,
      "end_time": 313346.0,
      "text": "because there&#39;s a translation gap between the reality of the story"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 313370.0,
      "end_time": 316792.0,
      "text": "and our consciousness interpreting the story"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 316816.0,
      "end_time": 318830.0,
      "text": "into our reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 319810.0,
      "end_time": 323157.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m using the word \"consciousness\" as a feeling of reality that we get"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 323181.0,
      "end_time": 326517.0,
      "text": "from our senses experiencing the world around us."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 328580.0,
      "end_time": 331377.0,
      "text": "Virtual reality bridges that gap."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 331985.0,
      "end_time": 336198.0,
      "text": "Now, you are on the tundra hunting with the clan leader."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 336222.0,
      "end_time": 338575.0,
      "text": "Or you are the clan leader."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 338600.0,
      "end_time": 341302.0,
      "text": "Or maybe you&#39;re even the woolly mammoth."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 341326.0,
      "end_time": 342961.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 346218.0,
      "end_time": 347830.0,
      "text": "So here&#39;s what special about VR."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 348726.0,
      "end_time": 350305.0,
      "text": "In all other mediums,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 350329.0,
      "end_time": 352599.0,
      "text": "your consciousness interprets the medium."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 353440.0,
      "end_time": 357214.0,
      "text": "In VR, your consciousness is the medium."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 358399.0,
      "end_time": 360833.0,
      "text": "So the potential for VR is enormous."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 360857.0,
      "end_time": 362531.0,
      "text": "But where are we now?"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 362555.0,
      "end_time": 365141.0,
      "text": "What is the current state of the art?"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 366318.0,
      "end_time": 367467.0,
      "text": "Well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 368746.0,
      "end_time": 369935.0,
      "text": "we are here."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 370724.0,
      "end_time": 373872.0,
      "text": "We are the equivalent of year one of cinema."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 373896.0,
      "end_time": 375522.0,
      "text": "This is the Lumière Brothers film"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 375546.0,
      "end_time": 378905.0,
      "text": "that allegedly sent a theater full of people running for their lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 378929.0,
      "end_time": 381222.0,
      "text": "as they thought a train was coming toward them."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 382136.0,
      "end_time": 385412.0,
      "text": "Similar to this early stage of this medium,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 385436.0,
      "end_time": 388977.0,
      "text": "in VR, we also have to move past the spectacle"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 389100.0,
      "end_time": 390887.0,
      "text": "and into the storytelling."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 390911.0,
      "end_time": 392658.0,
      "text": "It took this medium decades"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 392682.0,
      "end_time": 395340.0,
      "text": "to figure out its preferred language of storytelling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 395364.0,
      "end_time": 397140.0,
      "text": "in the form of a feature film."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 397164.0,
      "end_time": 400518.0,
      "text": "In VR today, we&#39;re more learning grammar"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 400542.0,
      "end_time": 401832.0,
      "text": "than writing language."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 402880.0,
      "end_time": 406431.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve made 15 films in the last year at our VR company, Vrse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 406455.0,
      "end_time": 408720.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;ve learned a few things."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 408801.0,
      "end_time": 412116.0,
      "text": "We found that we have a unique, direct path into your senses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 412140.0,
      "end_time": 414949.0,
      "text": "your emotions, even your body."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 415897.0,
      "end_time": 417572.0,
      "text": "So let me show you some things."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 417596.0,
      "end_time": 418994.0,
      "text": "For the purpose of this demo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 419180.0,
      "end_time": 422820.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re going to take every direction that you could possibly look,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 422107.0,
      "end_time": 424320.0,
      "text": "and stretch it into this giant rectangle."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 425830.0,
      "end_time": 427330.0,
      "text": "OK, here we go."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 429642.0,
      "end_time": 433923.0,
      "text": "So, first: camera movement is tricky in VR."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 433947.0,
      "end_time": 436490.0,
      "text": "Done wrong, it can actually make you sick."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 436930.0,
      "end_time": 441429.0,
      "text": "We found if you move the camera at a constant speed in a straight line,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 441453.0,
      "end_time": 443669.0,
      "text": "you can actually get away with it, though."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 443694.0,
      "end_time": 445421.0,
      "text": "The first day in film school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 445445.0,
      "end_time": 448320.0,
      "text": "they told me you have to learn every single rule"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 448560.0,
      "end_time": 449813.0,
      "text": "before you can break one."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 449838.0,
      "end_time": 452120.0,
      "text": "We have not learned every single rule."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 452360.0,
      "end_time": 453564.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve barely learned any at all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 453588.0,
      "end_time": 455405.0,
      "text": "but we&#39;re already trying to break them"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 455429.0,
      "end_time": 457957.0,
      "text": "to see what kind of creative things we can accomplish."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 457982.0,
      "end_time": 461694.0,
      "text": "In this shot here, where we&#39;re moving up off the ground, I added acceleration."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 461718.0,
      "end_time": 464551.0,
      "text": "I did that because I wanted to give you a physical sensation"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 464575.0,
      "end_time": 465957.0,
      "text": "of moving up off the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 465982.0,
      "end_time": 468475.0,
      "text": "In VR, I can give that to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 469797.0,
      "end_time": 473871.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 475882.0,
      "end_time": 479429.0,
      "text": "Not surprisingly, music matters a lot in this medium as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 479842.0,
      "end_time": 481716.0,
      "text": "It guides us how to feel."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 482354.0,
      "end_time": 485675.0,
      "text": "In this project we made with the New York Times, Zach Richter"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 485699.0,
      "end_time": 487454.0,
      "text": "and our friend, JR,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 487478.0,
      "end_time": 489363.0,
      "text": "we take you up in a helicopter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 489387.0,
      "end_time": 493325.0,
      "text": "and even though you&#39;re flying 2,000 feet above Manhattan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 493349.0,
      "end_time": 494937.0,
      "text": "you don&#39;t feel afraid."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 494961.0,
      "end_time": 497869.0,
      "text": "You feel triumphant for JR&#39;s character."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 499220.0,
      "end_time": 500501.0,
      "text": "The music guides you there."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 500525.0,
      "end_time": 502525.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 509364.0,
      "end_time": 510971.0,
      "text": "Contrary to popular belief,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 510995.0,
      "end_time": 513661.0,
      "text": "there is composition in virtual reality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 513683.99999999994,
      "end_time": 515745.99999999994,
      "text": "but it&#39;s completely different than in film,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 515770.0,
      "end_time": 517495.0,
      "text": "where you have a rectangular frame."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 517519.0,
      "end_time": 520300.0,
      "text": "Composition is now where your consciousness exists"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 520539.99999999994,
      "end_time": 522099.99999999994,
      "text": "and how the world moves around you."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 522927.0,
      "end_time": 526291.0,
      "text": "In this film, \"Waves of Grace,\" which was a collaboration between Vrse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 526315.0,
      "end_time": 529224.0,
      "text": "the United Nations, Gabo Arora, and Imraan Ismail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 529248.0,
      "end_time": 532490.0,
      "text": "we also see the changing role of the close-up in virtual reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 533139.0,
      "end_time": 537352.0,
      "text": "A close-up in VR means you&#39;re actually close up to someone."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 537954.0,
      "end_time": 540597.0,
      "text": "It brings that character inside of your personal space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 540621.0,
      "end_time": 544466.0,
      "text": "a space that we&#39;d usually reserve for the people that we love."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 544490.0,
      "end_time": 547660.0,
      "text": "And you feel an emotional closeness to the character"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 547684.0,
      "end_time": 550391.0,
      "text": "because of what you feel to be a physical closeness."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 556639.0,
      "end_time": 560978.0,
      "text": "Directing VR is not like directing for the rectangle."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 561200.0,
      "end_time": 564850.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s more of a choreography of the viewer&#39;s attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 564864.0,
      "end_time": 567458.0,
      "text": "One tool we can use to guide your attention"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 567482.0,
      "end_time": 568915.0,
      "text": "is called \"spatialized sound.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 568939.0,
      "end_time": 571906.0,
      "text": "I can put a sound anywhere in front of you, to left or right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 571931.0,
      "end_time": 573310.0,
      "text": "even behind you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 573334.0,
      "end_time": 576329.0,
      "text": "and when you turn your head, the sound will rotate accordingly."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 576354.0,
      "end_time": 579856.0,
      "text": "So I can use that to direct your attention to where I want you to see."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 580308.0,
      "end_time": 582886.0,
      "text": "Next time you hear someone singing over your shoulder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 582910.0,
      "end_time": 584170.0,
      "text": "it might be Bono."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 584195.0,
      "end_time": 585402.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 590539.0,
      "end_time": 593294.0,
      "text": "VR makes us feel like we are part of something."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 594459.0,
      "end_time": 597968.0,
      "text": "For most of human history, we lived in small family units."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 597992.0,
      "end_time": 599502.0,
      "text": "We started in caves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 599527.0,
      "end_time": 602960.0,
      "text": "then moved to clans and tribes, then villages and towns,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 602984.0,
      "end_time": 605676.0,
      "text": "and now we&#39;re all global citizens."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 606211.0,
      "end_time": 610110.0,
      "text": "But I believe that we are still hardwired to care the most"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 610350.0,
      "end_time": 612531.0,
      "text": "about the things that are local to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 613325.0,
      "end_time": 618283.0,
      "text": "And VR makes anywhere and anyone feel local."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 618307.0,
      "end_time": 620815.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why it works as an empathy machine."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 620839.0,
      "end_time": 624630.0,
      "text": "Our film \"Clouds Over Sidra\" takes you to a Syrian refugee camp,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 624870.0,
      "end_time": 628638.0,
      "text": "and instead of watching a story about people over there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 628662.0,
      "end_time": 632485.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s now a story about us here."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 634386.0,
      "end_time": 635896.0,
      "text": "But where do we go from here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 636432.0,
      "end_time": 638889.0,
      "text": "The tricky thing is that with all previous mediums,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 638913.0,
      "end_time": 641283.0,
      "text": "the format is fixed at its birth."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 642182.0,
      "end_time": 644710.0,
      "text": "Film has been a sequence of rectangles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 644950.0,
      "end_time": 646934.0,
      "text": "from Muybridge and his horses to now."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 647377.0,
      "end_time": 648926.0,
      "text": "The format has never changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 649654.0,
      "end_time": 653101.0,
      "text": "But VR as a format, as a medium,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 654370.0,
      "end_time": 655619.0,
      "text": "isn&#39;t complete yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 656767.0,
      "end_time": 659966.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not using physical celluloid or paper or TV signals."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 659990.0,
      "end_time": 663809.0,
      "text": "It actually employs what we use to make sense of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 664642.0,
      "end_time": 668545.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re using your senses as the paints on the canvas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 668569.0,
      "end_time": 669891.0,
      "text": "but only two right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 671653.0,
      "end_time": 675493.0,
      "text": "Eventually, we can see if we will have all of our human senses employed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 675517.0,
      "end_time": 679712.0,
      "text": "and we will have agency to live the story in any path we choose."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 680575.0,
      "end_time": 683310.0,
      "text": "And we call it virtual reality right now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 683550.0,
      "end_time": 685848.0,
      "text": "but what happens when we move past simulated realities?"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 687345.0,
      "end_time": 688775.0,
      "text": "What do we call it then?"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 689503.0,
      "end_time": 692339.0,
      "text": "What if instead of verbally telling you about a dream,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 692363.0,
      "end_time": 695137.0,
      "text": "I could let you live inside that dream?"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 695860.0,
      "end_time": 699487.0,
      "text": "What if instead of just experiencing visiting some reality on Earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 699511.0,
      "end_time": 703937.0,
      "text": "you could surf gravitational waves on the edge of a black hole,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 703961.0,
      "end_time": 706737.0,
      "text": "or create galaxies from scratch,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 706761.0,
      "end_time": 709844.0,
      "text": "or communicate with each other not using words"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 709869.0,
      "end_time": 711772.0,
      "text": "but using our raw thoughts?"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 713254.0,
      "end_time": 715335.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s not a virtual reality anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 716520.0,
      "end_time": 718398.0,
      "text": "And honestly I don&#39;t know what that&#39;s called."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 718884.0,
      "end_time": 721216.0,
      "text": "But I hope you see where we&#39;re going."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 722629.0,
      "end_time": 726351.0,
      "text": "But here I am, intellectualizing a medium I&#39;m saying is experiential."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 726839.0,
      "end_time": 728265.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s experience it."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 728845.0,
      "end_time": 732400.0,
      "text": "In your hands, you hopefully hold a piece of cardboard."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 733143.0,
      "end_time": 734776.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s open the flap."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 734800.0,
      "end_time": 737333.0,
      "text": "Tap on the power button to unlock the phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 738145.0,
      "end_time": 739769.0,
      "text": "For the people watching at home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 739793.0,
      "end_time": 741629.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re going to put up a card right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 741653.0,
      "end_time": 744883.0,
      "text": "to show you how to download this experience on your phone yourself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 744907.0,
      "end_time": 748208.0,
      "text": "and even get a Google cardboard of your own to try it with."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 749275.0,
      "end_time": 751802.0,
      "text": "We played in cardboard boxes as kids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 751826.0,
      "end_time": 756410.0,
      "text": "and as adults, I&#39;m hoping we can all find a little bit of that lightning"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 756434.0,
      "end_time": 759208.0,
      "text": "by sticking our head in one again."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 761615.0,
      "end_time": 763440.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re about to participate"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 763680.0,
      "end_time": 767520.0,
      "text": "in the largest collective VR viewing in history."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 768236.0,
      "end_time": 771854.0,
      "text": "And in that classic old-timey style of yesteryear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 771878.0,
      "end_time": 774109.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re all going to watch something"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 774133.0,
      "end_time": 776130.0,
      "text": "at the exact same time, together."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 777190.0,
      "end_time": 778442.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s hope it works."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 778466.0,
      "end_time": 780651.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s the countdown look like? I can&#39;t see."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 784564.0,
      "end_time": 791558.0,
      "text": "Audience: ...15, 14, 13, 12, 11, 10, 9,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 791582.0,
      "end_time": 798446.0,
      "text": "8, 7, 6, 5, 4, 3, 2, 1"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 802327.0,
      "end_time": 806155.0,
      "text": "(Birds singing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 814508.0,
      "end_time": 817168.0,
      "text": "(Train engine)"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 825351.0,
      "end_time": 827351.0,
      "text": "Audience: (Shreiks)"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 843285.0,
      "end_time": 844574.0,
      "text": "(Video) JR: Let me tell you"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 844599.0,
      "end_time": 847760.0,
      "text": "how I shot the cover of the New York Times Magazine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 847100.0,
      "end_time": 849194.0,
      "text": "\"Walking New York.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 858577.0,
      "end_time": 861987.0,
      "text": "I just got strapped on outside the helicopter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 862110.0,
      "end_time": 866255.0,
      "text": "and I had to be perfectly vertical so I could grab it."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 866279.0,
      "end_time": 867897.0,
      "text": "And when I was perfectly above --"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 867921.0,
      "end_time": 870658.0,
      "text": "you know, with the wind, we had to redo it a few times --"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 870682.0,
      "end_time": 872476.0,
      "text": "then I kept shooting."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 879598.0,
      "end_time": 881295.0,
      "text": "(Video) Woman&#39;s voice: Dear Lord,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 881900.0,
      "end_time": 883220.0,
      "text": "protect us from evil,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 884654.0,
      "end_time": 885865.0,
      "text": "for you are the Lord,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 887440.0,
      "end_time": 888231.0,
      "text": "the light."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 893824.0,
      "end_time": 896207.0,
      "text": "You who gave us life took it away."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 898191.0,
      "end_time": 899771.0,
      "text": "Let your will be done."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 900941.0,
      "end_time": 905505.0,
      "text": "Please bring peace to the many who have lost loved ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 905529.0,
      "end_time": 907272.0,
      "text": "Help us to live again."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 910564.0,
      "end_time": 913683.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 929660.0,
      "end_time": 930527.0,
      "text": "(Video) (Children&#39;s voices)"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 931504.0,
      "end_time": 936169.0,
      "text": "Child&#39;s voice: There are more kids in Zaatari than adults right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 941924.0,
      "end_time": 943953.0,
      "text": "Sometimes I think"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 943977.0,
      "end_time": 946411.0,
      "text": "we are the ones in charge."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 951410.0,
      "end_time": 952785.0,
      "text": "Chris Milk: How was it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 952809.0,
      "end_time": 956524.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 956548.0,
      "end_time": 959477.0,
      "text": "That was a cheap way of getting you to do a standing ovation."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 959501.0,
      "end_time": 962309.0,
      "text": "I just made you all stand. I knew you&#39;d applaud at the end."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 962333.0,
      "end_time": 963973.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 963998.0,
      "end_time": 967817.0,
      "text": "I believe that everyone on Earth needs to experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 967841.0,
      "end_time": 969421.0,
      "text": "what you just experienced."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 970360.0,
      "end_time": 973203.0,
      "text": "That way we can collectively start to shape this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 973227.0,
      "end_time": 975100.0,
      "text": "not as a tech platform"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 975250.0,
      "end_time": 976600.0,
      "text": "but as a humanity platform."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 977498.0,
      "end_time": 980682.0,
      "text": "And to that end, in November of last year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 980706.0,
      "end_time": 983992.0,
      "text": "the New York Times and Vrse made a VR project called \"The Displaced.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 984160.0,
      "end_time": 986362.0,
      "text": "It launched with one million Google Cardboards"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 986386.0,
      "end_time": 989858.0,
      "text": "sent out to every Sunday subscriber with their newspaper."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 989883.0,
      "end_time": 992401.0,
      "text": "But a funny thing happened that Sunday morning."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 992425.0,
      "end_time": 993747.0,
      "text": "A lot of people got them"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 993771.0,
      "end_time": 997977.0,
      "text": "that were not the intended recipients on the mailing label."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 998100.0,
      "end_time": 1001545.0,
      "text": "And we started seeing this all over Instagram."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 1005590.0,
      "end_time": 1006238.0,
      "text": "Look familiar?"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 1008250.0,
      "end_time": 1010393.0,
      "text": "Music led me on a path"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 1010420.0,
      "end_time": 1013469.0,
      "text": "of searching for what seemed like the unattainable"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 1013490.0,
      "end_time": 1014743.0,
      "text": "for a very long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 1015470.0,
      "end_time": 1019441.0,
      "text": "Now, millions of kids just had the same formative experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 1019460.0,
      "end_time": 1021201.0,
      "text": "in their childhood"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 1021230.0,
      "end_time": 1023534.0,
      "text": "that I had in mine."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 1024319.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1026548.9999999999,
      "text": "Only I think this one"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 1026569.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1027726.9999999999,
      "text": "surpasses it."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 1028359.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1029509.9999999999,
      "text": "Let&#39;s see"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 1029859.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1031901.9999999999,
      "text": "where this"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 1031569.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1032719.9999999999,
      "text": "leads them."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 1033380.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1034531.0000000001,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 1034560.0,
      "end_time": 1041401.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}